expression.expression-string: result['Flower'].sort {|a,b| index_a = in_order_months.index(a.downcase) index_a = 0 if index_a.nil? index_b = in_order_months.index(b.downcase) index_b = 0 if index_b.nil? index_b <=> index_a}
result['Flower'].sort {|a,b| index_a = in_order_months.index(a.downcase) index_a = 0 if index_a.nil? index_b = in_order_months.index(b.downcase) index_b = 0 if index_b.nil? index_a <=> index_b}
result['Flower'].sort {|a,b| index_a = in_order_months.index(a.downcase).to_i index_b = in_order_months.index(b.downcase).to_i index_a <=> index_b}
result[key] = result[key].sort {|a,b| index_a = in_order_months.index(a.downcase).to_i index_b = in_order_months.index(b.downcase).to_i index_a <=> index_b}
